tags.name:
place-holder
Placeholder for a piece of media in the future
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `place-holder`
 * @customElement place-holder
 * Placeholder for a piece of media in the future
 *
 * @demo demo/index.html
 *
 * @microcopy - the mental model for this element
 * - placeholder is a grey block on the page which can respond to drag and drop
 */

attributes.name: iconFromType
attributes.description: calculate an icon based on the type that was used

attributes.name: calcText
attributes.description: Calculate text based on the type in the event we have no default.

properties.name: iconFromType
properties.description: calculate an icon based on the type that was used

properties.name: calcText
properties.description: Calculate text based on the type in the event we have no default.
